description:
Stellar Extractor for Windows Backup is a fully automated backup recovery solution, designed to deal with inaccessible backup files created using Windows utilities and help users restore entire content from corrupt or damaged BKF, ZIP, VHDX and .FD files.

Stellar Extractor for Windows Backup is a fully automated backup recovery solution, designed to deal with inaccessible backup files created using Windows utilities and help users restore entire content from corrupt or damaged BKF, ZIP, VHDX and .FD files.
- Supports recovery of corrupt Backup files (VHDX, BKF, ZIP, FD)
- Recovers Backup files created using NTBackup, HP data protector and Backup Exec by Symantec
- Supports backup files created using Windows 10, 8.1, 7, Vista, XP, 2003 and 2000
- Restores all the instance of inaccessible data from selected backup file
- Saves the scanned output in a .DAT file format for later use
